26
00:01:33,133 --> 00:01:36,477
Putting it all together, we get the complete time-dependent

27
00:01:36,577 --> 00:01:40,096
Schrödinger equation. This beautiful equation tells us how the

28
00:01:40,196 --> 00:01:43,190
wave function psi evolves in time, given the system's

29
